Normal bump maps are added to material shaders by use of the [Bumpmap\_(Material\_global\_keyword).html Bumpmap] keyword or the [Blend\_(Material\_stage\_keyword).html Blend] keyword with the "bumpmap" parameter. As convention it's recommended that you add "\_local" to the end of the texture's filename.

